org.elasticsearch.painless

Class FunctionRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.painless.FunctionRef

  • public class FunctionRef
extends java.lang.Object
    Reference to a function or lambda.

    Once you have created one of these, you have "everything you need" to call LambdaMetaFactory either statically from bytecode with invokedynamic, or at runtime from Java.
